body:
Why is it changed to a different color altogether, it isn&#039;t a helpful change whatsoever
While you are at it, make more colours for the status indicator, right now it&#039;s just the old &quot;Green = online, Blue (yellow on live) = in something, Red = away&quot;
I suggest make it like: Green = Online, Blue = In Queue, Yellow = In Champ Select and In Game, Red = Away&quot;
It lets me know on a quick glance  if I can just PM my in queue friend to join his lobby, if they already have the new yellow indicator up I won&#039;t need to doublecheck
